reviewText: Great program very interesting to say the least always inspires me to be a pilot. I'd recommend this wonderful video anytime
If you enjoy watching videos about airline pilots and their planes, this is one you'll like.

I'm a HUGE fan, of Justplanes DVD, I own about 25-28 DVDs from them. I bouoght this one, because of the price (I think I paid $10 bucks for this). It's a great DVD to watch, you get a great view from the cockpit, watching the pilots perform their duties. Cool to watch the take off and landings, from the cockpit. I think you would enjoy this DVD!
